IMAPAccount sjtu
Host mail.sjtu.edu.cn
User mingkaidong@sjtu.edu.cn
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.secrets/sjtu-mailpass.gpg"
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs Login
# CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-bundle.crt

IMAPStore sjtu-remote
Account sjtu

MaildirStore sjtu-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mails/mbsyncmail/sjtu/
Inbox ~/mails/mbsyncmail/sjtu/INBOX

Channel sjtu
Far :sjtu-remote:
Near :sjtu-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

